    PeriodicTable.PeriodicTable — Module.

    The PeriodicTable module exports an elements variable that stores data (of type Element) on every element in the periodic table.

    The data can be looked up by atomic number via elements[n], by name (case-insensitive) via e.g. elements["oxygen"], or by symbol via e.g. elements[:O].
